<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   POLITICAL NEWS (``p'' category)
</P>
<P>
   BUSH-FORBES (Waterloo, Iowa) _ Texas Gov. George W. Bush and
publishing scion Steve Forbes held dueling rallies here on the eve
of the Iowa caucuses. Bush won the endorsement of the state's
leading newspaper, the Des Moines Register. And the Register's
latest statewide poll shows Bush ahead of Forbes by 23 percentage
points, 43 percent to 20 percent. By DAN FREEDMAN.
</P>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service/Washington
</P>
</TEXT>
