<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-23 22:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4223 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-FBN-VECSEY-COLUMN-NYT     01-23 0814
