<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-23 23:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4365 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-TEN-AUSTRALIAN-OPEN-N     01-23 0693
