<HEADLINE>
IOWA CAUCUSES MORE ABOUT EXPECTATIONS THAN OUTCOMES 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 SCOTT CANON  
 c. 1999 The Kansas City Star  
<TEXT>
